"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Small vessel disease in hypertrophic cardiomyopathy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 382px; height: 252px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Patients with hypertrophic cardiomyopathy often have small vessel disease which may be associated with symptoms of ischemia. The small intramural vessels often demonstrate apparent lumenal narrowing, caused by hypertrophy of the tunica media.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of Professor Michael Davies, St. George's Hospital, London.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
